  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GOOOOOOOOOOOOOOAL!</h2>Misha imagines he's playing soccer. It helps him win in any situation. In a card game, a fight, a chess match. It's no wonder they call him the Grandmaster GOOOOAL.<br><br>Win, score, place your bets and help Misha save up for a ticket to the big game.<br>The enemy never rests, if you lose, Misha will return home with an empty piggy bank. Powerful soccer balls with special effects and various mini-games boosting Misha's GOOOOOOAL will aid you in the struggle.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2>Collect and upgrade powerful balls and bonuses to defeat the bosses Misha will encounter on his journey.<br>Explore the level and level up your GOOOOAL day by day.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058090/extras/3a37bc77cc54914bd5f1eaba800396bf.poster.avif?t=1721391064\" width=362 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058090/extras/3a37bc77cc54914bd5f1eaba800396bf.webm?t=1721391064\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058090/extras/3a37bc77cc54914bd5f1eaba800396bf.mp4?t=1721391064\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
